---
title: Quick Beef, Currant & Pistachio Rissoles with Beetroot Relish, Radish Salad & Kumara Fries
description: Let’s go a little crazy with these rissoles because who said dinner can’t be fun. Blow you mind (and tastebuds) by adding a dose of
pistachio nutty goodness and currants to these beef rissoles. Keep the party going with a serving of bright kumara fries, perfect
for dipping in a herby mayo. You’ll be having a ball of fun!
